    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391460/extras/da33ff59c1d23bcc9364056c32b1fdbd.avif?t=1769718514\" width=780 height=82 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>一场灾难性的事件粉碎了一个强大的灵魂，将其分裂成两个较小的实体，将其巨大的力量散落到世界各地。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>这两个灵魂必须踏上旅程，找回失去的一切，因为他们被共同的使命所束缚。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>你将同时操控这两个角色克服考验揭开共同命运背后的真相。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391460/extras/52ab1fcca7b901acf4ec3d386a793a5e.poster.avif?t=1769718514\" width=780 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391460/extras/52ab1fcca7b901acf4ec3d386a793a5e.webm?t=1769718514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391460/extras/52ab1fcca7b901acf4ec3d386a793a5e.mp4?t=1769718514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391460/extras/d130baa5be2523eba182aecd4604e952.avif?t=1769718514\" width=780 height=82 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>同时指导两个角色使用 相同的移动键。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>一同时行动，另一同时紧随其后.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>他们必须携手未来的挑战。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391460/extras/c8dbf036c48f1d6ec6673e6a05f0df2d.poster.avif?t=1769718514\" width=780 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391460/extras/c8dbf036c48f1d6ec6673e6a05f0df2d.webm?t=1769718514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391460/extras/c8dbf036c48f1d6ec6673e6a05f0df2d.mp4?t=1769718514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391460/extras/9db4514d4e2d1ccf46e68e0a339e1d57.avif?t=1769718514\" width=780 height=82 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>探索劲爆手工制作环境每一间都充满了细节和独特的氛围。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>每一章都展开了一个引人入胜的故事, 邀请你去发现隐藏的秘密和经验一个充满活力的世界.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391460/extras/3da242051f11e93c71bc466826962502.poster.avif?t=1769718514\" width=780 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391460/extras/3da242051f11e93c71bc466826962502.webm?t=1769718514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391460/extras/3da242051f11e93c71bc466826962502.mp4?t=1769718514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391460/extras/3ec069499d729b423234fa7d5b90d8fd.avif?t=1769718514\" width=780 height=82 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>在你的旅程中，发现和解锁新的能力。 每项能力都能为你提供新颖、富有创意的应对挑战的方法，助你克服前进道路上的种种困难。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391460/extras/9eb29387d64094ef04f467a35b3a943a.poster.avif?t=1769718514\" width=780 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391460/extras/9eb29387d64094ef04f467a35b3a943a.webm?t=1769718514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391460/extras/9eb29387d64094ef04f467a35b3a943a.mp4?t=1769718514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
